%% ML Metadata (MLMD) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>gRPC Client
    participant DSPUI as DSP UI<br/>gRPC Client
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306 or 5432/TCP<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifact, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol, Optional TLS<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Query Result
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecution Response
    deactivate MLMD

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts (trained model, dataset)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifact records<br/>OCC support
    DB-->>MLMD: Query Result
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifacts Response
    deactivate MLMD

    DSP->>MLMD: PutEvents (link artifacts to executions)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT event records
    DB-->>MLMD: Query Result
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutEvents Response
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over DSPUI,DB: Flow 2: Artifact Lineage Query

    DSPUI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph (artifact_id)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT lineage graph traversal<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol, Optional TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage Records
    MLMD-->>DSPUI: GetLineageSubgraph Response<br/>(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)
    deactivate MLMD

    DSPUI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext (pipeline_run_id)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts by context
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact Records
    MLMD-->>DSPUI: GetArtifactsByContext Response
    deactivate MLMD
